Vite : Tool that is used with mordern JS frameworks like vue.js and react

@php
use Illuminate\Support\Facades\Vite;
@endphp
 
<!doctype html>
<head>
    {{-- ... --}}
 
    <style>
        {!! Vite::content('resources/css/app.css') !!}
    </style>
    <script>
        {!! Vite::content('resources/js/app.js') !!}
    </script>
</head>

If we build the front end using the react,we need vit.js pulgins
npm install --save-dev @vitejs/plugin-react

